<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Eye</defName><label>ocular bloom</label><description>FEV flora sharpens the host's sight.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statOffsets><ShootingAccuracyPawn>0.08</ShootingAccuracyPawn></statOffsets></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Ear</defName><label>resonant canopy</label><description>FEV flora heightens the host's threat perception.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statOffsets><MeleeHitChance>0.05</MeleeHitChance></statOffsets></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Nose</defName><label>spore scent</label><description>FEV flora filters hostile chemicals through scent membranes.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statFactors><ToxicResistance>1.20</ToxicResistance></statFactors></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Jaw</defName><label>thornbite</label><description>FEV flora hardens the jaw into a brief combat bloom.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statOffsets><MeleeDPS>0.20</MeleeDPS></statOffsets></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Tongue</defName><label>nectar speech</label><description>FEV flora sweetens the host's voice and scent.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statOffsets><SocialImpact>0.15</SocialImpact></statOffsets></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Arm</defName><label>vine surge</label><description>FEV flora floods the arm with gripping vine strength.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statOffsets><MeleeDPS>0.35</MeleeDPS></statOffsets></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Hand</defName><label>root touch</label><description>FEV flora steadies the host's fingers for careful tending.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statOffsets><MedicalTendQuality>0.05</MedicalTendQuality></statOffsets></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Leg</defName><label>springvine stride</label><description>FEV flora launches the host into a short burst of speed.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statOffsets><MoveSpeed>0.30</MoveSpeed></statOffsets></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Foot</defName><label>clinging roots</label><description>FEV flora anchors the host's steps and improves movement.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statOffsets><MoveSpeed>0.18</MoveSpeed></statOffsets></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Spine</defName><label>braced trunk</label><description>FEV flora braces the host's spine against strain.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statOffsets><MoveSpeed>0.12</MoveSpeed><MentalBreakThreshold>-0.03</MentalBreakThreshold></statOffsets></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Stomach</defName><label>root digestion</label><description>FEV flora purges hostile matter from the gut.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statFactors><ToxicResistance>1.15</ToxicResistance></statFactors></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Heart</defName><label>heartwood pulse</label><description>FEV flora drives a living immune pulse through the host.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statFactors><ImmunityGainSpeed>1.15</ImmunityGainSpeed></statFactors></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Lung</defName><label>green breath</label><description>FEV flora filters the host's breath through living membranes.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statFactors><ToxicResistance>1.20</ToxicResistance></statFactors></li></stages></HediffDef>
<HediffDef><defName>WestTek_NumenBuff_Kidney</defName><label>deep filtration</label><description>FEV flora accelerates the host's blood filtration.</description><isBad>false</isBad><stages><li><statFactors><ToxicResistance>1.25</ToxicResistance></statFactors></li></stages></HediffDef>

